virtmail.m4 has been tested at the followings:
 sendmail) 8.13.8, 8.14.3, 8.14.4
 dovecot)  1.2.9 - 1.2.16
 procmail) 3.22
 maildrop) 2.3.0.20100112, 2.5.1, 2.5.2, 2.5.3

